item.title: Broken Cache
item.dc:creator: @Fox0wnage Fox0wnage
item.description:
@Fox0wnage wrote:

The correct term is “Damaged Cache”. My client has one too, but I don’t mind since all of my areas in my server aren’t around the places where the messed up models are.
To fix it you can download a cache and replace yours. Use the search bar and type: Aeolian Cache
download it and replace your cache with it. It also has some features which I personally don’t like but you may like them.

Good luck.
